<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FFB06A0FF82F91D6177DB314" pageId="75" pageNumber="833" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="C42B36FEFFB06A0FF82F91D6177DB314" blockId="75.[2001,2596,1816,2244]" pageId="75" pageNumber="833">
Originally described as G. curry: but subsequently corrected to 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFFB06A0FF6F591E31762BCE5" authorityName="Eger &amp; Schlitter" authorityYear="2001" box="[2313,2402,1978,2007]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Glauconycteris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="75" pageNumber="833" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="curryae">curryae</taxonomicName>
. A. Hassanin and colleagues in 2018 retrieved 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFFB06A0FF65E91871424BCCD" authorityName="Eger &amp; Schlitter" authorityYear="2001" box="[2466,2596,2014,2047]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Glauconycteris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="75" pageNumber="833" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="curryae">G. curryae</taxonomicName>
as sister to 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFFB06A0FF7989E5C16D8B314" authorityName="Thomas" authorityYear="1901" box="[2148,2264,2053,2086]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Glauconycteris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="75" pageNumber="833" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="beatrix">G. beatrix</taxonomicName>
. Monotypic.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FFB06A0FF82D9E75140DB347" pageId="75" pageNumber="833" type="distribution">
<caption id="90EB6676FFB06A0FF82D9E75140DB347" ID-DOI="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6398091" ID-Zenodo-Dep="6398091" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6398091/files/figure.png" inLine="true" pageId="75" pageNumber="833" targetBox="[1387,1978,1824,2238]" targetPageId="75">
