<emphasis id="F6E0EAECFFB06A0FF82D9E75167AB37F" bold="true" box="[2001,2170,2092,2125]" pageId="75" pageNumber="833">Distribution.</emphasis>
Known only from S 
<collectingCountry id="BC83766EFFB06A0FF6749E75141AB37F" box="[2440,2586,2092,2125]" name="Cameroon" pageId="75" pageNumber="833">Cameroon</collectingCountry>
